388
00:38:19,417 --> 00:38:21,510
- Don't jump in the water!
- Simon, don't!

389
00:38:21,586 --> 00:38:25,181
- No, don't!
- Simon, don't go!

390
00:38:43,775 --> 00:38:46,642
