392
00:38:52,417 --> 00:38:54,817
Get out of the water, Simon!

393
00:39:35,493 --> 00:39:37,552
Shoot him!

394
00:39:37,628 --> 00:39:39,220
Rudy, behind you!

395
00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:45,428
Swim, Simon! Swim!

396
00:39:45,503 --> 00:39:47,266
No! Liberty!

397
00:40:20,071 --> 00:40:21,095
Shoot it!

398
00:40:21,172 --> 00:40:24,266
What do you think I'm trying
to do, you fucking moron?

399
00:40:52,036 --> 00:40:53,663
Come on.
Come on.

400
00:40:55,673 --> 00:40:58,938
Fuck! You fucking zombie bastards!

401
00:40:59,010 --> 00:41:02,138
You're not gonna fuck with us again,
are ya, asshole?

402
00:41:02,213 --> 00:41:04,545
Are you? Are you?

