00:41:12,523 --> 00:41:14,753
- My face!
- You all right? Let me see.

404
00:41:14,825 --> 00:41:17,123
Let me see.
Could I have your coat?

405
00:41:17,195 --> 00:41:20,562
- Oh, fuck!
- Here, let me see it. Let me look.

406
00:41:20,631 --> 00:41:22,326
Fuck!

